OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,FResidents in Cleckheaton have called
OL,7,Ffor work on a housing development to
OL,8,Fstop immediately due to fears over
OL,9,Fasbestos.
OL,11,FSince construction work began on the
OL,12,Fsite of the former asbestos factory
OL,13,Foff Westgate in May, residents have
OL,14,Ftold ITV Calendar that six people
OL,15,Fliving nearby now need inhalers and
OL,16,Ffour have been referred to hospital
OL,17,Ffor chest X-Rays.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/14
