OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,FThe developer, Strata Homes, is
OL,7,Fplanning to build 180 homes at the
OL,8,Fsite. They say the work is being
OL,9,Fcarried out safely and in line with
OL,10,Fregulations.
OL,12,FKirklees Council says it is taking
OL,13,Fresidents' concerns seriously and is
OL,14,Fanalysing dust emissions to make sure
OL,15,Fthey're at a safe level.
OL,17,FHowever, residents are so concerned
OL,18,Fabout the possibility of asbestos that
OL,19,Fthey sent their own samples away to be
OL,20,Ftested and have told ITV that asbestos
OL,21,Fwas found in five out of seven samples.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/14
