OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,FAt a public meeting that was held at
OL,7,FSt Luke's Church on the 6 August,
OL,8,Fresidents were told by the council's
OL,9,Fpublic protection department that soil
OL,10,Fsampling was done across the site with
OL,11,Fasbestos fibres found in four soil
OL,12,Fsamples.
OL,14,FHowever, they were also told that this
OL,15,Fis "not uncommon" and that the
OL,16,Fmeasures they took were in line with
OL,17,Fappropriate guidelines.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/14
