OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,FDespite this, local resident Tracy
OL,7,FWeaver said that she believes that
OL,8,Fsince work began there's been a rise
OL,9,Fin illness in the area.
OL,11,FShe said, "We have six people on
OL,12,FClaire Road alone that are new to
OL,13,Finhalers, me included. (...) We've got
OL,14,Fa nine-year-old who's never had any
OL,15,Fasthma or breathing difficulties, he's
OL,16,Fnow on two sets of inhalers.
