OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,F"We've got a two-year-old with a
OL,7,Fblocked lung. We've got people needing
OL,8,Fstronger prescriptions for existing
OL,9,Fconditions, four of us have been
OL,10,Freferred to hospital for a chest x-
OL,11,Fray, I'm one of them. It just needs
OL,12,Fstopping until an investigation and an
OL,13,Finquiry."
OL,15,FMesothelioma UK says that asbestos
OL,16,Fshould never be found in household
OL,17,Fdust.
