OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,FHowever, they added that there's a
OL,7,Flong gestation period for asbestos
OL,8,Frelated illnesses so any recent health
OL,9,Fproblems are unlikely to be as a
OL,10,Fresult of the asbestos.
OL,12,FCEO of Mesothelioma UK Liz Darlison
OL,13,Fsaid, "If it's a site of an old
OL,14,Fasbestos works then big red flag. It
OL,15,Fneeds completely remediating before it
OL,16,Fshould ever be used. I mean how can
OL,17,Fyou let your children play in a garden
OL,18,Fthat might have asbestos in it?"
