OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,FCouncillor Kath Pinnock told ITV
OL,7,FCalendar that "This town has a very
OL,8,Ftragic history of asbestos related
OL,9,Fillnesses and deaths. No way am I
OL,10,Fgoing to allow that to be repeated."
OL,12,FAt the meeting, officers from Kirklees
OL,13,FCouncil told residents that they
OL,14,Fhadn't been aware that there used to
OL,15,Fbe an asbestos factory on the site.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/14
