OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,FHowever, since the meeting the council
OL,7,Fhave announced it's going to carry out
OL,8,Fextra air quality testing around the
OL,9,Fsite following the concerns raised by
OL,10,Fresidents, despite current testing
OL,11,Fshowing asbestos being managed
OL,12,Feffectively at the site.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said, "The council has
OL,15,Falso pledged to step up its efforts to
OL,16,Fensure all the conditions to control
OL,17,Fdust and manage contaminated land are
OL,18,Fbeing followed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/14
