OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,F"Like many building sites in Kirklees,
OL,7,Fand across the country, there are
OL,8,Fhazardous chemicals in the ground that
OL,9,Fneed to be managed carefully. That's
OL,10,Fwhy we've ordered these extra tests to
OL,11,Frespond to what residents have seen
OL,12,Fand address their understandable
OL,13,Fworries.
OL,15,F"We will carry out this thorough
OL,16,Ftesting as quickly as we can and
OL,17,Freport the results back to residents
OL,18,Fbefore deciding what, if any, further
OL,19,Faction is needed."
