OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,FIn the meantime they say they're going
OL,7,Fto monitor the site closely.
OL,9,FThe Thirteen Group took on the site
OL,10,Fafter planning permission was granted
OL,11,Fin October 2023 and says "work is
OL,12,Fprogressing in a phased and controlled
OL,13,Fmanner, in line with the remediation
OL,14,Fplan approved by Kirklees Council, and
OL,15,Fin full compliance with national
OL,16,Fregulations."
