OL,6,F"The contractor continues to manage
OL,7,Fdust through approved mitigation
OL,8,Fmethods, has monitoring in place, and
OL,9,Fis in regular dialogue with the HSE
OL,10,Fand Kirklees Council to ensure work is
OL,11,Fcarried out safely."
OL,13,FIn a statement responding to concerns
OL,14,Ffrom residents, Strata Homes said: "We
OL,15,Ftake the health and safety of our site
OL,16,Fteams, neighbouring residents, and the
OL,17,Fwider community extremely seriously.
