OL,3,CCleckheaton residents call for housing
OL,4,Cwork to stop amid asbestos fears
OL,6,F"Following recent assessments, we are
OL,7,Fpleased to confirm that the Health and
OL,8,FSafety Executive (HSE) has visited the
OL,9,Fsite and found no cause for concern.
OL,11,F"In line with our commitment to
OL,12,Fresponsible construction, we continue
OL,13,Fto manage dust on-site using approved
OL,14,Fmitigation methods.
OL,16,F"We remain in ongoing dialogue with
OL,17,Fboth the HSE and Kirklees Council to
OL,18,Fensure all works are carried out
OL,19,Fsafely, and with due care for the
OL,20,Flocal environment and community."
