OL,7,Fit "visited the site to assess
OL,8,Fcontrols and have requested further
OL,9,Fdocumentation regarding monitoring
OL,10,Fboth at source and background as part
OL,11,Fof our enquiries."
OL,13,FHSE confirmed that it is also working
OL,14,Fwith the council to make sure
OL,15,Fappropriate controls are in place.
